keepCenteredToUserLocation

public final void keepCenteredToUserLocation(boolean on)
Sets whether to center the map to user's location update with sensors. To center the map to the user's location only for once, use centerToUserLocation() method.

Parameters:
on - A flag to turn this feature on.

centerToUserLocation

public final void centerToUserLocation()
Center the map to user's location for one time. To make the map continuously follow the user's location, use keepCenteredToUserLocation(boolean on) method.
